    Obtain HPA release information

    getHpaDate.Rd

    Obtain release information about the HPA data, including version, release data and Ensembl version the data is based on. Detailed release information is accessed on-line using browseURL.

    getHpaDate()
getHpaVersion()
getHpaEnsembl()

    Value

    A character.

    References

    HPA release history: http://www.proteinatlas.org/about/releases

    Author

    Laurent Gatto <lg390@cam.ac.uk>

    Examples

    getHpaVersion()
#> version 
#>  "21.0" 
getHpaDate()
#>         date 
#> "2021.11.18" 
getHpaEnsembl()
#>  ensembl 
#> "103.38"
